drupalNodeEvent.title: NEXTChina - Election 2020: A new era in U.S.- China relations?

field_speakers.processed: Craig Allen, Kaiser Kuo, Jane Sun, Yasheng Huang, Susan Thornton, Yuen Yuen Ang, Jeremy Goldkorn, Joseph Zeng, James Green, Evan Feigenbaum,David Sandalow, Gary Rieschel, Alex Wang

field_description.processed:
By the time this online conference happens, one week will have passed since the election and the fate of the world’s next 4 years will have been sealed.
What will the results mean for China? What will they mean for the U.S.?
This year’s NEXTChina will gather together some of the world’s most leading experts on all things China as they discuss how the U.S. presidential election results will affect the next 4 years of geopolitics, and business.
